3 persons / with all amenities / kitchen, bath / paid by the employer. Accommodation near as possible to the place of work. The employer provides doyizd.Firma candidate provides meeting on arrival in Poland. Wages - from 16 to 19 zł net / hours of work (depending on skills and experience) Payment of salaries by the 10th of each month on the card account / open company. The work 10-12 hours a day from Mon - Sat on (depending on the project) .Robota in modern companies.', '10000', 0, '', '', 0, '2016-11-16 10:33:11', '', '', '', 1, '2016-11-16 08:33:11', '2016-11-16 08:33:11'),
